01:59.771 --> 02:01.338
Thank you, General Terne.

02:01.382 --> 02:03.035
Take a seat
with the wee ones.

02:03.079 --> 02:06.256
-Let the grownups talk, eh?

02:06.300 --> 02:07.692
Show us the trick again,
Kwan. Again.

02:07.736 --> 02:09.172
Not now. Beat it.

02:09.216 --> 02:10.565
Some news from Madrigal City.

02:10.608 --> 02:12.001
Two divisions of Marines
