02:28.452 --> 02:30.019
Aren'’t you handsome.

02:35.372 --> 02:36.591
Nice to meet you.

02:36.634 --> 02:37.940
I'’m Ruben. I'm--

02:37.983 --> 02:39.289
Ruben from Castra.

02:39.333 --> 02:40.856
