-He could lose his toes.
-Good.

28:00.069 --> 28:03.116
That'’ll teach him to think
before every step he takes.

28:06.206 --> 28:07.511
And the others?

28:07.555 --> 28:09.296
They got to learn.

28:09.339 --> 28:11.385
And what are they learning?

28:11.428 --> 28:13.213
Who'’s in charge,
for starters.

28:15.041 --> 28:16.477
I'’ve been too easy on 'em.

28:18.740 --> 28:21.743
Fear is a hell of a motivator.

28:21.787 --> 28:23.571
Trust me.

28:23.614 --> 28:24.746
Soren.

28:28.881 --> 28:31.361
-Soren.
-It'’s that girl.

28:31.405 --> 28:34.495
That pain-in-the-ass
little girl.

28:38.020 --> 28:39.630
Ah, shit,
it doesn'’t matter now.

28:39.674 --> 28:41.502
She'’s all alone out there.

28:41.545 --> 28:44.723
If the desert doesn'’t get her,
Vinsher'’s goons

28:44.766 --> 28:46.986
have probably already
found her and carved her up.

28:47.029 --> 28:49.423
Kwan Ha is alive.

28:49.466 --> 28:51.512
How do you know?

28:51.555 --> 28:54.820
Because Vinsher
just tripled the bounty.

28:56.735 --> 28:58.606
Tripled.

29:00.695 --> 29:02.044
That damn girl.

29:15.188 --> 29:17.581
-Agatha! Hello!
-Oh, hello!

29:17.625 --> 29:18.887
Come on.

29:22.673 --> 29:25.024
Ah, General...

29:25.067 --> 29:27.504
did I catch you
at a good time?

30:20.253 --> 30:21.863
Such a tragedy.

30:21.907 --> 30:23.473
So much death.

30:25.388 --> 30:26.868
And, in the end,

30:26.912 --> 30:29.915
it wasn'’t even the UNSC
that did Jin in.

30:29.958 --> 30:31.394
Stubborn fool.

30:31.438 --> 30:33.179
Never could tell
who his real friends were.

30:34.702 --> 30:36.747
Jin knew whom
he could trust...

30:38.010 --> 30:39.620
and who'’d betray him.

30:39.663 --> 30:41.709
It was his delusions
that betrayed him.

30:41.752 --> 30:45.669
Tell me, General,
and be honest,

30:45.713 --> 30:48.411
what good did Jin Ha do
for Madrigal?

30:48.455 --> 30:51.632
-He gave us pride.
-Pride?

30:51.675 --> 30:53.939
That'’s not a word
that I would associate

30:53.982 --> 30:56.767
with a colony
of hole-diggers.

30:57.899 --> 31:00.075
And what did this pride bring?

31:00.119 --> 31:02.773
Jin had them stop drilling
for the only resource

31:02.817 --> 31:05.124
their filthy planet produced
and take up arms.

31:05.167 --> 31:06.908
No. Not stop drilling.

31:06.952 --> 31:10.390
Just protect certain areas
for the people of Madrigal.

31:10.433 --> 31:11.608
Agatha...

31:12.958 --> 31:16.918
You and I knew
Jin Ha very well.

31:16.962 --> 31:18.311
This was a sick man,

31:18.354 --> 31:20.704
as was the whole Ha family.

31:20.748 --> 31:23.925
Sick, delusional, and weak.

31:23.969 --> 31:26.710
And yet you are
so deathly afraid of them.

31:35.719 --> 31:38.244
Where is the girl?

31:38.287 --> 31:41.160
Even if I knew,

31:41.203 --> 31:42.944
I wouldn'’t tell you.

31:45.251 --> 31:46.426
Boss.

31:55.043 --> 31:57.437
Now, if there'’s
nothing else you require,

31:57.480 --> 31:59.613
I really must get
my perishables stored.

32:00.744 --> 32:01.920
Yes, yes, of course.

32:11.146 --> 32:12.626
Fetch the car, Pete.

34:41.818 --> 34:43.037
What are you doing here?

34:43.081 --> 34:44.299
Like I told you,

34:44.343 --> 34:45.692
you owe me one ship

34:45.735 --> 34:47.259
and a shitload
of deuterium money.

34:47.302 --> 34:49.304
I'’m not going back
with you.

34:49.348 --> 34:51.219
You might want
to consider your options

34:51.263 --> 34:53.308
'’cause if I found you,
Vinsher can'’t be far behind.

34:53.352 --> 34:54.962
And he don'’t travel solo.

34:55.005 --> 34:57.530
Ah. It'’s the bounty
you'’re after?

34:57.573 --> 34:59.532
I don'’t work like that.

34:59.575 --> 35:01.403
That'’s exactly
how you work.

35:03.623 --> 35:05.103
You wanna insult me,

35:05.146 --> 35:06.626
or you gonna let me
save your ass?

35:08.193 --> 35:09.716
I'’m doing just fine
on my own, thanks.

35:09.759 --> 35:11.413
And yet, here we are.

35:13.763 --> 35:17.593
Look, maybe you'’re too young
or too stupid to understand,

35:17.637 --> 35:20.205
but I made a promise to John
to keep you safe,

35:20.248 --> 35:22.120
and I intend to keep it,
whether I like you or not.

35:26.254 --> 35:28.038
You'’re not exactly
a picnic either.

35:28.082 --> 35:29.997
My pistol.

35:31.694 --> 35:34.306
-Oh, it'’s like that?
-Yeah, it'’s like that.

35:34.349 --> 35:35.829
-You just have to be difficult.
-Me?

35:35.872 --> 35:37.744
-You should talk!
-Kwan!

35:37.787 --> 35:39.224
Damn it.

35:39.267 --> 35:40.834
Let'’s move.

35:40.877 --> 35:42.270
Kwan Ha!

35:43.445 --> 35:46.274
Last of the Has.

35:46.318 --> 35:49.495
The pernicious hour
is at last upon us.

35:51.192 --> 35:54.152
Time to put away
childish things.

35:54.195 --> 35:57.503
There is no hope for escape.

35:57.546 --> 35:59.200
Okay.

35:59.244 --> 36:02.029
Sit your ass down,
stay low,

36:02.072 --> 36:03.726
and start killing people.

36:03.770 --> 36:04.988
You'’ll die.

36:05.032 --> 36:06.207
Not a chance.

36:06.251 --> 36:08.166
We'’ll both die.

36:08.209 --> 36:09.819
You got a better idea?

36:09.863 --> 36:11.430
'’Cause they're coming in fast.

36:12.996 --> 36:14.389
Let them come.

36:14.433 --> 36:16.130
Say what, now?

36:16.174 --> 36:18.654
All the hydrogen gas
runs through here

36:18.698 --> 36:21.048
to the main Sky Pipe
out there.

36:21.091 --> 36:23.224
We fill up the pipe
and then shoot it.

36:23.268 --> 36:26.140
Bam, the whole place
goes up in flames.

36:26.184 --> 36:28.882
-No more Vinsher.
-And no more us.

36:28.925 --> 36:30.840
There'’s a steel vault
a hundred feet across the way.

36:30.884 --> 36:32.973
-I see it.
-As long as we'’re inside

36:33.016 --> 36:35.976
the vault when the pipe
explodes, we'’re probably safe.

36:36.019 --> 36:37.369
Probably.

36:37.412 --> 36:39.588
You wanted a plan?
That'’s it.

36:39.632 --> 36:43.505
If we are going to fight,
we meet them on my terms.

36:43.549 --> 36:46.334
The people
of Madrigal need you!

36:48.945 --> 36:50.251
-Come out.
-All right.

36:50.295 --> 36:51.774
Join us!

36:51.818 --> 36:53.950
Long as I still get to kill
some people.

36:53.994 --> 36:55.343
No harm will come to you.

36:55.387 --> 36:57.998
Of that, I give you
my solemn word.

37:01.480 --> 37:03.569
I loved your father, Kwan.

37:05.658 --> 37:07.268
He was like a brother to me.

37:12.230 --> 37:14.580
This is Kwan Ha,

37:14.623 --> 37:16.799
daughter of Jin Ha.

37:18.279 --> 37:20.673
Madrigal does not
belong to you.

37:20.716 --> 37:23.371
It does not belong
to the UNSC.

37:23.415 --> 37:26.113
It belongs to the people
of Madrigal.

37:27.854 --> 37:31.379
I don'’t want to fight you,
but I will never...

37:32.467 --> 37:34.252
never surrender.

37:34.295 --> 37:35.992
Also, Vinsher...

37:37.124 --> 37:40.606
my dad hated you.

37:41.694 --> 37:42.782
Send them in.

37:58.580 --> 38:00.930
-Uh-oh.
-What do you mean, "uh-oh"?

38:00.974 --> 38:02.671
The gas isn'’t flowing.

38:02.715 --> 38:04.456
Why not?

38:04.499 --> 38:06.458
The valve at the base
