38:06.501 --> 38:08.242
I'’ll have to open it manually.

38:08.286 --> 38:09.852
I'’ll open the valve.

38:09.896 --> 38:11.941
-You go to the vault.
-No! I'’ll open it.

38:11.985 --> 38:14.422
Oh, okay. You.

38:14.466 --> 38:16.163
You won'’t make it 10 feet
out there.

38:16.206 --> 38:18.296
I know another way.

38:21.864 --> 38:24.171
Soon as I get the gas flowing,
I'’ll make a break for the vault.

38:24.214 --> 38:25.868
Count to five
and take the shot

38:25.912 --> 38:27.566
right at the base
