38:27.609 --> 38:29.959
-Got it?
-Yeah.

38:30.003 --> 38:31.918
Make sure you'’re in the vault
when the pipe explodes.

38:31.961 --> 38:33.441
Yeah, yeah, yeah, yeah,
I know, boom.

38:35.313 --> 38:36.401
Oh...

38:38.011 --> 38:39.839
You'’ve got to be kidding me.

38:41.362 --> 38:42.885
Told you I was rich.

38:54.810 --> 38:56.464
Hold your fire!

38:58.727 --> 39:01.077
We got '’em surrounded!

39:01.121 --> 39:02.688
Clear the building!

39:02.731 --> 39:04.559
Eyes up there.
I need eyes there.

39:06.692 --> 39:09.172
Hey. See you at the vault?

39:09.216 --> 39:11.566
Save a bullet
for the Sky Pipe.

39:16.571 --> 39:18.617
Fan out!

39:36.852 --> 39:38.376
So these are the aliens.

39:39.638 --> 39:40.987
Ugly bastards.

39:41.030 --> 39:42.423
Let'’s go, let's go!

39:47.297 --> 39:48.211
Go left!

39:55.784 --> 39:57.307
Pirate!

40:15.282 --> 40:16.588
Where is he?!

40:42.788 --> 40:45.051
Okay... this way.

41:16.822 --> 41:18.693
He'’s over here!

41:43.370 --> 41:45.198
He'’s everywhere, boss.

41:45.241 --> 41:47.069
-And the girl?
-I don'’t know.

41:47.113 --> 41:48.680
Get the girl!

42:02.737 --> 42:04.391
Look back there!

42:28.284 --> 42:29.895
She'’s right there!

42:43.604 --> 42:45.040
Right there! Right there!

43:06.235 --> 43:07.585
Save one for the Sky Pipe.

43:09.369 --> 43:10.500
This better work.

43:36.526 --> 43:37.615
I got her!

43:52.542 --> 43:53.892
What the hell is this?

43:53.935 --> 43:55.676
Get this thing off me.

43:55.720 --> 43:57.330
Where are you going?

43:57.373 --> 43:58.418
Damn it--

44:15.261 --> 44:16.784
Hold your fire!

44:23.748 --> 44:25.358
Kwan!

44:27.665 --> 44:32.408
Your adventure has come
to its inevitable conclusion.

44:35.411 --> 44:36.717
Come now.

44:38.937 --> 44:40.634
Show yourself.

44:43.506 --> 44:48.337
Let us end this contretemps
with some degree of dignity.

44:56.781 --> 44:59.871
And what of you,
poor Soren?

45:01.263 --> 45:03.526
Thou proud aspirer.

45:03.570 --> 45:05.180
Failed Spartan,

45:05.224 --> 45:07.052
mediocre pirate,

45:07.095 --> 45:11.056
and now martyr for the delusion
of an orphaned young girl.

45:14.059 --> 45:16.235
What kind of fool
does that make you?

45:17.845 --> 45:20.543
