47:21.142 --> 47:22.622
It'’s more
than we agreed to,

47:22.665 --> 47:25.625
and you'’re gonna
need some.

47:25.668 --> 47:27.018
I owe you one ship,

47:27.061 --> 47:28.802
plus a shitload
of deuterium money.

47:28.846 --> 47:30.108
Consider us even.

47:31.544 --> 47:32.719
Yeah, okay.

47:35.591 --> 47:36.723
I could use you...

47:37.855 --> 47:39.030
for whatever comes next.

47:39.073 --> 47:40.292
I'’m sure you could.

47:40.335 --> 47:41.902
But I got my own thing going,

47:41.946 --> 47:45.601
and I'’m not one
